    .grid.grid--line
      .grid__cell.unit-1-2.content
        markdown:
          ## Asset pipeline

            1. You can require any asset from component.

            1. The `main` asset defined in `component.json` is going to be aliased to name of the component.

        p.notice.notice--important.content--small
